# Design system — contrast on theme-independent surfaces

Our color tokens `--text-primary`, `--accent-primary`, `--text-inverse` **invert** between
light and dark themes. Some backgrounds — lime and pure white — do **not** invert: they
stay light in both themes. Pairing a theme-aware text token with a theme-independent
light surface produces light-on-light text in dark mode (invisible).

## Rules

1. For solid `bg-accent-lime` / `bg-accent-lime-hover` surfaces, **always** use
   `text-accent-lime-text` for text/icons.
2. For solid `bg-white` / `bg-white/NN` surfaces, **always** use `text-on-light` for text.
3. For solid dark surfaces that never invert (e.g. custom dark overlays like `bg-black/40`),
   use `text-on-dark`.
4. **Never** pair `text-accent-primary` / `text-text-primary` / `text-text-inverse`
   with a solid lime or white background.
5. Tint variants (`bg-accent-lime/15`, `bg-accent-lime/20`, etc.) are translucent and
   inherit the surface underneath — they may use theme-aware text tokens.

## Tokens (defined in `platform-app/src/app/globals.css`)

- `--text-on-light: #0F172A` — fixed dark, for light surfaces. Exposed as
  Tailwind class `text-on-light`.
- `--text-on-dark:  #F1F5F9` — fixed light, for dark surfaces. Exposed as
  Tailwind class `text-on-dark`.
- `--accent-lime-text: #1A2E05` — existing, preferred for any lime surface.
  Exposed as `text-accent-lime-text`.

## Safety net

`globals.css` contains a `@layer base` rule that applies `--text-on-light` to
`.bg-accent-lime`, `.bg-accent-lime-hover`, and `.bg-white` by default. Explicit
Tailwind `text-*` utilities (higher cascade layer) still win, so this only helps
when a contributor forgets to specify text color — it does **not** replace the
rules above.

## Quick examples

Good:

```tsx
<button className="bg-accent-lime-hover text-accent-lime-text hover:bg-accent-lime">
  Новая сессия
</button>

<button className="bg-white/90 hover:bg-white text-on-light">
  Редактировать
</button>
```

Bad (white-on-lime / white-on-white in dark mode):

```tsx
<button className="bg-accent-lime-hover text-accent-primary">
  Новая сессия
</button>

<button className="bg-white/90 text-text-primary">
  Редактировать
</button>
```
